headline.main: Myanmar Says Ethnic Rebels Stage Raid on Northeastern Town
headline.print_headline: Myanmar Says Ethnic Rebels Stage Raid on Northeastern Town

lead_paragraph: Myanmar says at least 30 people were killed in fighting triggered by a pre-dawn attack by an ethnic rebel group in the country's northeast bordering China.
